## Limitations

The findings are based on available literature and may not cover all aspects of how greed influences budget decisions. The influence of greed can vary significantly across different industries and organizational cultures, which may not be fully captured in the sources reviewed. Additionally, the complexity of human behavior and organizational dynamics means that the impact of greed on budgeting is multifaceted and may not be entirely predictable.

